name: KnuVoice Security Solutions
tagline: Use your voice to access your mobile devices with this awesome new App from KnuVoice.com!
body:
The KnuVoice App is the inaugural project from KnuVoice Security Solutions, with one goal: We want to make it EASIER for people to access their Mobile Devices, using the latest in Voice Recognition technology, actually IMPROVING safety and security while eliminating the need for passwords, patterns, and pins!

Interested Developers please contact us!


### Authors and Contributors
@KnuVoice
